history.content:
I enrolled in a class A and was accepted. I then swapped it for a class B, which I was put on the waitlist for. I later dropped class A.

I know that if I add class A again, the swap will become active again, so if I'm later accepted off the waitlist of B, I'll be dropped from A. However, if I am enrolled off of the waitlist of B first, and then later add A: will I be enrolled in both classes, or will it drop me from B (even though I was already accepted off the waitlist)?
history.subject: Understanding swaps
